  "detailed_description": "In Tiny Traffic you solve puzzles by parking all cars safely. Move and rotate blocks to redirect the flow of traffic, keeping in mind that each level only has a limited amount of block-modifiers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445980/extras/bed380a93cb52f866b0757fb0ec30dcd.poster.avif?t=1667036987\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445980/extras/bed380a93cb52f866b0757fb0ec30dcd.webm?t=1667036987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445980/extras/bed380a93cb52f866b0757fb0ec30dcd.mp4?t=1667036987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The movement is turn-based, but all cars move at the same time, requiring you to think ahead.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445980/extras/d2ca0e1608bf79518f1d7f8129928c2e.poster.avif?t=1667036987\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445980/extras/d2ca0e1608bf79518f1d7f8129928c2e.webm?t=1667036987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445980/extras/d2ca0e1608bf79518f1d7f8129928c2e.mp4?t=1667036987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 45 hand-crafted levels.<br></li><li> Progression; 4 different chapters, increasing in difficulty and complexity.<br></li><li> Zen-like visuals and audio, letting you unwind.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "In Tiny Traffic you solve puzzles by parking all cars safely. Move and rotate blocks to redirect the flow of traffic, keeping in mind that each level only has a limited amount of block-modifiers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445980/extras/bed380a93cb52f866b0757fb0ec30dcd.poster.avif?t=1667036987\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445980/extras/bed380a93cb52f866b0757fb0ec30dcd.webm?t=1667036987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445980/extras/bed380a93cb52f866b0757fb0ec30dcd.mp4?t=1667036987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The movement is turn-based, but all cars move at the same time, requiring you to think ahead.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445980/extras/d2ca0e1608bf79518f1d7f8129928c2e.poster.avif?t=1667036987\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445980/extras/d2ca0e1608bf79518f1d7f8129928c2e.webm?t=1667036987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445980/extras/d2ca0e1608bf79518f1d7f8129928c2e.mp4?t=1667036987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 45 hand-crafted levels.<br></li><li> Progression; 4 different chapters, increasing in difficulty and complexity.<br></li><li> Zen-like visuals and audio, letting you unwind.</li></ul>",
